    "ChatGPT was used as a coding assistant for the elaboration of the results and the experiments.",
    "The table shows the F1 scores (across individual insight comparisons) and Pearson correlation coefficients (of the final ELO score of all models) between evaluators and domain expert on the private dataset.",
